metadata.description:
BABA YAGA

This is the most detailed work I've ever drawn!
-Total number of details: 55**

-Retired former hitman John Wick /aka Baba Yaga, leads a good life, but when he loses his wife to an incurable disease. The most valuable asset left to him from his wife is his dog. One day, 3 gangsters break into his house, kill his dog and hijack his car. John Wick will take revenge on them. The striking scenes in the 4 movies of the John Wick series and all the places and items that John Wick is associated with are depicted in all details in this drawing.
metadata.name: BABA YAGA #1/7
